				<h1><a href="http://maybemaimed.com/">Maybe Maimed but Never Harmed</a></h1>
				<p>Kill all humans.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

<div id="content" class="col620">


	<div class="post-1894 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-politics-of-sex category-writing-and-blogging tag-media tag-sex-negative-patterns clear" id="post-1894">
		        <div class="social-media-buttons col140" style="text-align: right;">
            <iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fmaybemaimed.com%2F2010%2F08%2F10%2Fhow-sex-negative-lies-perpetuate-a-fear-based-culture%2F&amp;layout=box_count&amp;show_faces=true&amp;width=55&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=62" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:55px; height:62px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
